# Cost Control Rules

Do not scan the whole repository unless explicitly approved.

Prefer:
- narrow file inspection
- targeted grep/find
- batched reads
- concise summaries
- targeted builds/tests

Avoid:
- node_modules
- dist
- coverage
- cache
- generated files
- large logs
- repeated reads of unchanged files
- broad test suites without approval
